<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Futsal Booking System</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="bg-success text-white text-center py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Futsal Booking System</h1>
    <p class="lead">Book your favorite futsal court online and enjoy the game!</p>
    <a href="#bookings" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Book Now</a>
  </header>

  <section class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card bg-success text-white">
          
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Futsal with Security</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Enjoy your futsal game with peace of mind. Our futsal court is equipped with top-notch security measures, ensuring a safe and secure environment for you and your team. Focus on the game and let us take care of your security concerns.The futsal has CCTV services</p>
           
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card bg-success text-white">
          
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Big Field Futsal</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Experience the thrill of playing futsal on our spacious and expansive futsal court. With a larger playing area, you and your team will have ample space to showcase your skills, engage in intense matches, and enjoy the game to the fullest. Get ready for an unforgettable futsal experience!</p>
        
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card bg-success text-white">
        
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Affordable Price Futsal</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Enjoy your favorite futsal game without breaking the bank. Our futsal court offers affordable prices, ensuring that everyone can participate in this thrilling sport without any financial burden. Experience the joy of playing futsal at a pocket-friendly cost. Don't miss out on the fun!</p>
          
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3">
    <p>&copy; 2023 Futsal Booking System. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <!-- Bootstrap JavaScript -->
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
